    {
      "id": "PopularPost334632",
      "post_content": "Maybe I'm not understanding something here but I thought you couldn't counter their counter with this enchantment because the rules state \"When the triggered ability resolves, it creates a copy of that spell for each other player.\" They original counter has already resolved so how can you counter it?  \n  \nAlso I want to know how this card effects [Corrupt](/Pages/Card/Details.aspx?name=Corrupt). Do the copying players have to have swamps or is it taken off the original cast?",
      "posted_by": "beer2328",
      "html": "<div class=\"post evenItem\" id=\"PopularPost334632\" style=\"background-color: rgba(255,255,255,0.08);\">\n<span class=\"postContent\" id=\"ctl00_ctl00_ctl00_MainContent_SubContent_SubContent_popularPosts_postsRepeater_ctl06_post\">Maybe I'm not understanding something here but I thought you couldn't counter their counter with this enchantment because the rules state \"When the triggered ability resolves, it creates a copy of that spell for each other player.\" They original counter has already resolved so how can you counter it?<br/><br/>Also I want to know how this card effects <a class=\"autoCard\" data:cardname=\"Corrupt\" href=\"/Pages/Card/Details.aspx?name=Corrupt\">Corrupt</a>. Do the copying players have to have swamps or is it taken off the original cast?</span>\n<div class=\"postDetails\" id=\"ctl00_ctl00_ctl00_MainContent_SubContent_SubContent_popularPosts_postsRepeater_ctl06_postDetails\" style=\"padding-top: 5px;\">\n<div class=\"reportAbuse\">\n<a href=\"../../Classes/Controls/#\" id=\"ctl00_ctl00_ctl00_MainContent_SubContent_SubContent_popularPosts_postsRepeater_ctl06_reportAbuseLink\" onclick=\"HandleReportPost(this, '334632'); return false;\">\r\n                                    Report Abuse</a>\u00a0\u00a0\r\n                                    \r\n                            </div>\n<div class=\"postedBy\">\r\n                                Posted By: \r\n                                <span id=\"PostedBy100685\">beer2328</span>\r\n                                (8/11/2013 10:38:23 PM)\r\n                            </div>\n<div class=\"postRating\">\n<div class=\"postRatingLabel\">\r\n                                    Rating:\u00a0\r\n                                </div>\n<div style=\"float: left;\">\n<div class=\"starRating\" id=\"ctl00_ctl00_ctl00_MainContent_SubContent_SubContent_popularPosts_postsRepeater_ctl06_postRating_starRating\"><img alt=\"0.5\" src=\"../../Images/Stars/LeftClearSmall.png\"/><img alt=\"1.0\" s