      "id": "PopularPost365258",
      "post_content": "In a game with multiple players, or special rules I would rate this a 3/5  \nIn a 1v1 this easily gets a 5/5  \n  \nthis coupled with [curse of exhaustion](/Pages/Card/Details.aspx?name=curse of exhaustion) is pretty much a giant f\\*ck you  \n  \n*of course that means the match is at least turn 4. (unless you use banned stuff like [black lotus](/Pages/Card/Details.aspx?name=black lotus)) And by then you should have won*  \n  \nDisregard that, anyone who actually thinks by turn 5 you should have won is an idiot and needs to stop playing magic.",
