    {
      "id": "PopularPost371116",
      "post_content": "This is part of the cycle of Curses (without Green, there were no green Curses) that are older symmetric enchantments made one-sided. This one is [Hive Mind](/Pages/Card/Details.aspx?name=Hive Mind) (albeit this one says \"may\"). The others are [Curse of Death's Hold](/Pages/Card/Details.aspx?name=Curse of Death's Hold) ([Night of Souls' Betrayal](/Pages/Card/Details.aspx?name=Night of Souls' Betrayal)), [Curse of Bloodletting](/Pages/Card/Details.aspx?name=Curse of Bloodletting) ([Furnace of Rath](/Pages/Card/Details.aspx?name=Furnace of Rath)), and [Curse of Exhaustion](/Pages/Card/Details.aspx?name=Curse of Exhaustion) ([Rule of Law](/Pages/Card/Details.aspx?name=Rule of Law)).",
      "posted_by": "legendary_orp",
      "html": "<div class=\"post oddItem\" id=\"PopularPost371116\">\n<span class=\"postContent\" id=\"ctl00_ctl00_ctl00_MainContent_SubContent_SubContent_popularPosts_postsRepeater_ctl09_post\">This is part of the cycle of Curses (without Green, there were no green Curses) that are older symmetric enchantments made one-sided. This one is <a class=\"autoCard\" data:cardname=\"Hive Mind\" href=\"/Pages/Card/Details.aspx?name=Hive Mind\">Hive Mind</a> (albeit this one says \"may\"). The others are <a class=\"autoCard\" data:cardname=\"Curse of Death's Hold\" href=\"/Pages/Card/Details.aspx?name=Curse of Death's Hold\">Curse of Death's Hold</a> (<a class=\"autoCard\" data:cardname=\"Night of Souls' Betrayal\" href=\"/Pages/Card/Details.aspx?name=Night of Souls' Betrayal\">Night of Souls' Betrayal</a>), <a class=\"autoCard\" data:cardname=\"Curse of Bloodletting\" href=\"/Pages/Card/Details.aspx?name=Curse of Bloodletting\">Curse of Bloodletting</a> (<a class=\"autoCard\" data:cardname=\"Furnace of Rath\" href=\"/Pages/Card/Details.aspx?name=Furnace of Rath\">Furnace of Rath</a>), and <a class=\"autoCard\" data:cardname=\"Curse of Exhaustion\" href=\"/Pages/Card/Details.aspx?name=Curse of Exhaustion\">Curse of Exhaustion</a> (<a class=\"autoCard\" data:cardname=\"Rule of Law\" href=\"/Pages/Card/Details.aspx?name=Rule of Law\">Rule of Law</a>).</span>\n<div class=\"postDetails\" id=\"ctl00_ctl00_ctl00_MainContent_SubContent_SubContent_popularPosts_postsRepeater_ctl09_postDetails\" style=\"padding-top: 5px;\">\n<div class=\"reportAbuse\">\n<a href=\"http://wizards.custhelp.com/cgi-bin/wizards.cfg/php/enduser/ask.php?p_prods=522,706,739&amp;p_cats=\" id=\"ctl00_ctl00_ctl00_MainContent_SubContent_SubContent_popularPosts_postsRepeater_ctl09_reportAbuseLink\" onclick=\"HandleReportPost(this, '371116'); return false;\">\r\n                                    Report Abuse</a>\u00a0\u00a0\r\n                                \r\n                            </div>\n<div class=\"postedBy\">\r\n                                Posted By: \r\n                                <span id=\"PostedBy104383\">legendary_orp</span>\r\n                                (4/18/2014 11:11:18 PM)\r\n                            </div>\n<div class=\"postRating\">\n<div class=\"postRatingLabel\">\r\n                                    Rating:\u00a0\r\n                                </div>\n<div style=\"float: left;\">\n<div class=\"starRating\" id=\"ctl00_ctl00_ctl00_MainContent_SubContent_SubContent_popularPosts_postsRepeater_ctl09_postRating_starRating\"><img alt=\"0.5\" src=\"../../Images/Stars/LeftClearSmall.png\"/><img alt=\"1.0\" src=\"../../Images/Stars/RightClearSmall.png\"/><img alt=\"1.5\" src=\"../../Images/Stars/LeftClearSmall.png\"/><img alt=\"2.0\" src=\"../../Images/Stars/RightClearSmall.png\"/><img alt=\"2.5\" src=\"../../Images/Stars/LeftClearSmall.png\"/><img alt=\"3.0\" src=\"../../Images/Stars/RightClearSmall.png\"/><img alt=\"3.5\" src=\"../../Images/Stars/LeftClearSmall.png\"/><img alt=\"4.0\" src=\"../../Images/Stars/RightClearSmall.png\"/><img alt=\"4.5\" src=\"../../Images/Stars/LeftClearSmall.png\"/><img alt=\"5.0\" src=\"../../Images/Stars/RightClearSmall.png\"/>\n<br/>\n</div>\n</div>\n<br class=\"clear\"/>\n</div>\n<div class=\"postRating\">\n<div class=\"postRatingLabel\">\r\n                                    \u00a0\r\n                                </div>\n<div style=\"float: left;\">\n</div>\n<br class=\"clear\"/>\n</div>\n</div>\n<br class=\"clear\"/>\n</div>"
